Ziyi?

00:29:21.977 --> 00:29:25.000
(Hospital Haiwan Peliharaan Chongle)

00:29:26.160 --> 00:29:27.110
Chun Ge.

00:29:27.110 --> 00:29:29.200
Kalau kita betul-betul kawan,
tukar syif dengan saya.

00:29:29.200 --> 00:29:30.350
(Chun Ge)
Jangan cuba menipu saya.

